The code implements the Buckingham type vdW potential + Gaussian Charge PME interaction
in Lammps (version 2017-Aug11)
Designed for the hydrogen bonding polarizable (HBP) water force field
Hao Jiang, Othonas A Moultos, Ioannis George Economou and Athanassios Z Panagiotopoulos
Hydrogen-Bonding Polarizable Intermolecular Potential Model for Water
J. Phys. Chem. B, 120, 48, 12358
